We’re following up on our recent email. You reported that your dwelling was
damaged by the ac condensation line overflow on August 13, 2024. We’re
continuing to look into the facts of your claim to determine whether coverage is
provided by your policy for this loss.
While we research the claim and coverage, TRAVELERS PERSONAL INSURANCE
COMPANY reserves its rights under the policy and law, including the right to deny
all or part of your claim that is not covered. We’ve included the relevant policy
wording, which begins on the next page(s).
